<li><a href="http://home.dialix.com/~u3336/factory/index2.html" class="external text" title="http://home.dialix.com/~u3336/factory/index2.html" rel="nofollow">A Factory Discography</a> - Factory Records catalog by Dennis Remmer.</li>
<li><a href="http://home.dialix.com/~u3336/factory/facbn.html" class="external text" title="http://home.dialix.com/~u3336/factory/facbn.html" rel="nofollow">Factory Benelux Discography</a> - Factory Benelux section of the above website (scroll to FBN 24 to see The Wake).</li>
<li><a href="http://home.dialix.com/~u3336/factory/facuk3.html" class="external text" title="http://home.dialix.com/~u3336/factory/facuk3.html" rel="nofollow">FAC 101 to FAC 150</a> - Portion of Remmer's Factory catalog that contains FACT 130.</li>
<li><a href="http://sdrc.lib.uiowa.edu/dada/merz/8/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://sdrc.lib.uiowa.edu/dada/merz/8/index.htm" rel="nofollow">The full text of NASCI (Merz No. 8/9, Hanover, April-July 1924).</a></li>
</ul>
